      {
        "parameters": {
          "content": "## SYS 05 — Client Weekly Updates\n\n**Trigger:** Every Friday 4PM EST (cron).\n\n**What it does:** Loads all closed-won clients from HubSpot, checks for recent activity (last 7 days). If no activity, sends a Google Chat warning before sending. For each client, uses Claude to generate a weekly update email (what we did, what's next, items needed), then sends via Resend. Keeps clients informed and surfaces stale accounts.\n\n**Dependencies:** CONFIG, HubSpot, Call Claude API, Send Email, Send Google Chat Alert, Log.",
          "height": 320,
          "width": 460,
          "color": 5
        },
        "id": "note-sys08",
        "name": "Note — About this workflow",
        "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
